1. Allows only `https://app.example.com` and `https://admin.example.com` origins
2. Sets `Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true` for allowed origins
3. Echoes the specific origin (not wildcard) when credentials are used
4. Includes `Vary: Origin` header to prevent cache poisoning
5. Handles preflight OPTIONS requests with 204 status
6. Does NOT add CORS headers to the `/health` endpoint
7. Sets appropriate allowed methods, headers, and max-age for preflight

